{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777073964228,"sessionID":"ses_23e23a62affeOLCYKs5at8IiBV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_p7KrgufUH2CiSQMQMdQVgY1N","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"category":"quick","command":"analyze-mode","description":"Explore workspace capabilities","load_skills":[],"prompt":"You are analyzing D:\\agent_workspace in analysis mode. Quickly inspect the capability-library structure, especially mycli, skill-library, and any task-hall-related capability. Summarize relevant directories, existing patterns, and any clues about how task-hall is expected to be used. Keep it concise but concrete.","run_in_background":true,"session_id":"","subagent_type":""},"output":"Background task launched.\n\nBackground Task ID: bg_1e136ba9\nDescription: Explore workspace capabilities\nAgent: Sisyphus-Junior (category: quick)\nStatus: pending\n\nSystem notifies on completion. Use `background_output` with task_id=\"bg_1e136ba9\" to check.\n\nDo NOT call background_output now. Wait for <system-reminder> notification first.\n\n<task_metadata>\nsession_id: ses_23e233bb2ffeNj0DDJNhQZI2N1\ntask_id: bg_1e136ba9\nbackground_task_id: bg_1e136ba9\n</task_metadata>\n\nto continue: task(session_id=\"ses_23e233bb2ffeNj0DDJNhQZI2N1\", load_skills=[], run_in_background=false, prompt=\"...\")","metadata":{"truncated":false,"prompt":"You are analyzing D:\\agent_workspace in analysis mode. Quickly inspect the capability-library structure, especially mycli, skill-library, and any task-hall-related capability. Summarize relevant directories, existing patterns, and any clues about how task-hall is expected to be used. Keep it concise but concrete.","agent":"Sisyphus-Junior","category":"quick","load_skills":[],"description":"Explore workspace capabilities","run_in_background":true,"command":"analyze-mode","sessionId":"ses_23e233bb2ffeNj0DDJNhQZI2N1","model":{"providerID":"MoreCode","modelID":"gemini-3-flash"}},"title":"Explore workspace capabilities","time":{"start"